      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## TF-IDF"
      ],
      "id": "cf2f7b303a506ffc"
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8b9cbc9351429f2"
      },
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### Препроцессинг"
      ],
      "id": "8b9cbc9351429f2"
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "id": "3d4e95dc92c99c24"
      },
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "К TF-IDF, который подсчитывает количество слов, применим леммитазацию, чтобы разные формы слова считались одним целым"
      ],
      "id": "3d4e95dc92c99c24"
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "ExecuteTime": {
          "end_time": "2026-04-17T14:13:13.832953600Z",
          "start_time": "2026-04-17T14:13:10.140102700Z"
        },
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "273b8c96e363b723",
        "outputId": "523544b3-ccf3-40f4-a953-57b8f196950a"
      },
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import re\n",
        "import nltk\n",
        "from nltk.corpus import stopwords\n",
        "import pymorphy3\n",
        "\n",
        "# Загружаем стоп-слова (предлоги, союзы и т.д., которые не несут смысла)\n",
        "nltk.download('stopwords')\n",
        "stop_words = set(stopwords.words('russian')).union(set(stopwords.words('english')))\n",
        "\n",
        "morph = pymorphy3.MorphAnalyzer()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Создаем словарь(кэш), чтобы не лемматизировать одно и то же слово дважды\n",
        "lemma_cache = {}\n",
        "\n",
        "def clean_and_lemmatize(text):\n",
        "    text = str(text).lower()\n",
        "\n",
        "    text = re.sub(r'[^a-zа-яё]', ' ', text)\n",
        "\n",
        "    words = text.split()\n",
        "    lemmas = []\n",
        "\n",
        "    for w in words:\n",
        "        if w in stop_words:\n",
        "            continue # Пропускаем мусорные слова\n",
        "\n",
        "        if w not in lemma_cache:\n",
        "            # Лемматизируем только если слова нет в кэше\n",
        "            lemma_cache[w] = morph.parse(w)[0].normal_form\n",
        "\n",
        "        lemmas.append(lemma_cache[w])\n",
        "\n",
        "    return \" \".join(lemmas)"
      ],
      "id": "273b8c96e363b723",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stderr",
          "text": [
            "[nltk_data] Downloading package stopwords to /root/nltk_data...\n",
            "[nltk_data]   Unzipping corpora/stopwords.zip.\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "execution_count": 9
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "ExecuteTime": {
